<view class="container">
  <view class="page-body">
    <canvas id="myCanvas" type="2d" style="width: 100%; height: 360px"></canvas>
    <view class="btn-area">
      <button type="primary" bindtap="createOffscreenCanvas">create OffscreenCanvas</button>
      <button type="primary" bindtap="getContext">OffscreenCanvas.getContext</button>
    </view>
    <view class="page-section-title page-section-title-space">
      <text>点击 create OffscreenCanvas 按钮创建和当前上屏画布等宽等高的离屏画布；\n点击 OffscreenCanvas.getContext 在离屏画布上绘制矩形并渲染到当前上屏画布上；</text>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>